folder: Ten Eyck St. & Humboldt St., Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Ten Eyck St. - Humboldt St.
text:
Ten Eyck Street (left), north side, between Humboldt Street and Bushwick Ave., across demolition from Stagg Street. In the background at the N.E. corner of Bushwick Ave., and Ten Eyck Street, is St. Catherine's Hospital.

September 26, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
